    "body": "The debugger prints new lines incorrectly, because extra newline is inserted:\n\n```rust\nostd::miri_println!(\"argc={argc} argv={argv:p}\\nargs={args:?}\");\n```\n\n```\n┌Output\n│argc=\n│1\n│ argv=\n│0x\n│10018\n│\n│args=\n│[\n```\n\n\nThe desired output is\n```\n┌Output─────────────\n│argc=1 argv=0x10018\n│args=[0x1000c]\n```",
